    "Second, our study cohort consisted predominantly of patients with a high prevalence of heart failure and exclusion criteria were relatively rare.",
    "This composition was due to the structured query methodology used to create the patient list for the COPILOT-HF trial.",
    "While this approach is effective to narrow down the list of potentially eligible patients for the study and enable a more cost-effective approach to use LLMs, the results might exhibit variability when applied to the 13 different conditions in populations with varying prevalence of these conditions.",
    "A third limitation is that a single expert clinician prepared the gold standard.",
    "Including additional clinicians will help characterize variations in the expert reviews, and additionally provide a quality assurance for the gold standard."
